<!-- ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
     PAGE 4 — REMAINING TERMS, SIGNATURE & ACCEPTANCE
     ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<div class="top-bar"></div>
<div class="page-header">
  <div class="ph-left">{{company.name}} &nbsp;&mdash;&nbsp; Letter of Appointment</div>
  <div class="ph-right">{{employee.full_name}} &nbsp;|&nbsp; {{today}}</div>
</div>

<div class="body">

  <div class="tc-block">
    <div class="tc-clause-title"><span class="clause-num">13</span> Company Property &amp; Assets</div>
    <div class="tc-clause-body">All equipment, materials, data, software, access credentials, and assets
    provided to you for official use remain the sole property of <strong>{{company.name}}</strong>.
    You must use such assets solely for authorised business purposes, maintain them in good working condition,
    and return them in full on or before your last working day. Any loss, damage, or unauthorised use may
    result in recovery of the cost from your dues.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tc-block">
    <div class="tc-clause-title"><span class="clause-num">14</span> Transfer &amp; Relocation</div>
    <div class="tc-clause-body">The company may, at its discretion, transfer or depute you to any of its
    branch offices, subsidiaries, associated companies, client sites, or project locations anywhere within
    India or abroad, based on business requirements. Such transfer or relocation shall be communicated with
    reasonable notice and shall not be construed as a change in your terms of employment.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tc-block">
    <div class="tc-clause-title"><span class="clause-num">15</span> Performance Reviews &amp; Increments</div>
    <div class="tc-clause-body">Your performance will be formally reviewed at the end of the probation
    period and thereafter on an annual basis. Salary increments, bonuses, and promotions, if any, are
    solely at the discretion of management and are based on individual performance, business results,
    and market benchmarks. No increment shall be deemed automatic or guaranteed.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tc-block">
    <div class="tc-clause-title"><span class="clause-num">16</span> Social Media &amp; Communications Policy</div>
    <div class="tc-clause-body">You shall not post, share, or publish any content on social media or
    public platforms that could disparage, defame, or harm the reputation of <strong>{{company.name}}</strong>,
    its clients, employees, or partners. Any official communication on behalf of the company through
    external channels must receive prior written approval. Violation may result in disciplinary action
    or termination.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tc-block">
    <div class="tc-clause-title"><span class="clause-num">17</span> Termination &amp; Exit Process</div>
    <div class="tc-clause-body">
      <ul>
        <li>On separation (resignation, retirement, or termination), you are required to complete a structured exit process including knowledge transfer, handover of responsibilities and assets, clearance from all departments, and submission of resignation in writing.</li>
        <li>Full and Final Settlement (F&amp;F), including payment of any outstanding salary, leave encashment, or other dues, will be processed within <strong>45 working days</strong> of completion of exit formalities.</li>
        <li>Experience and Relieving Letters will be issued only upon completion of notice period, clearance, and receipt of all dues from the employee.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="tc-block">
    <div class="tc-clause-title"><span class="clause-num">18</span> Data Protection &amp; Privacy</div>
    <div class="tc-clause-body">You consent to the collection, processing, and storage of your personal
    data by <strong>{{company.name}}</strong> for legitimate employment purposes, as required by applicable
    data protection laws including the Digital Personal Data Protection Act, 2023. Such data shall not
    be shared with third parties without your consent, except where required by law.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tc-block">
    <div class="tc-clause-title"><span class="clause-num">19</span> Amendments &amp; Modifications</div>
    <div class="tc-clause-body">The company reserves the right to amend, modify, or update the terms
    and conditions of employment, including compensation structures, policies, and procedures, with
    reasonable prior notice. Continued employment after such notice shall constitute your acceptance
    of the revised terms. Any individual modification to this letter shall only be valid if executed
    in writing and signed by an authorised representative of the company.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tc-block">
    <div class="tc-clause-title"><span class="clause-num">20</span> Governing Law &amp; Jurisdiction</div>
    <div class="tc-clause-body">This letter and your employment with <strong>{{company.name}}</strong>
    shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of India. Any dispute, claim, or
    controversy arising out of or in connection with this letter or your employment shall be subject
    to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in
    <strong>{{#if company.city}}{{company.city}}{{else}}the city of the company's registered office{{/if}}</strong>.</div>
  </div>

  <div class="tc-block">
    <div class="tc-clause-title"><span class="clause-num">21</span> Entire Agreement</div>
    <div class="tc-clause-body">This letter, together with any documents expressly incorporated herein
    by reference, constitutes the entire agreement between you and <strong>{{company.name}}</strong>
    with respect to the subject matter hereof, and supersedes all prior discussions, representations,
    warranties, and understandings, whether oral or written. No prior negotiations or communications
    shall have any legal effect unless confirmed in this letter.</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Closing paragraph -->
  <p style="margin-top:12px;">
    We trust you will find this offer satisfactory and look forward to your long and successful
    association with <strong>{{company.name}}</strong>. This offer is valid for
    <strong>7 (seven) calendar days</strong> from the date of issuance. Kindly sign and return
    the acceptance copy along with the required documents to the HR Department at the earliest.
  </p>

  <!-- Company signature -->
  <div class="signature-block">
    <p style="font-size:11.5px; color:#475569; margin-bottom:14px;">Yours sincerely,<br>For <strong>{{company.name}}</strong></p>
    {{#if company.signature_url}}
      <img src="{{company.signature_url}}" alt="Signature" />
    {{/if}}
    {{#if company.stamp_url}}
      <img src="{{company.stamp_url}}" alt="Stamp" style="max-height:56px; max-width:56px; margin-left:auto; margin-bottom:4px; display:block;" />
    {{/if}}
    <div class="sig-name">{{company.signatory_name}}</div>
    <div class="sig-designation">{{company.signatory_designation}}</div>
    <div class="sig-company">{{company.name}}</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Acceptance by candidate -->
  <div class="acceptance-box">
    <div class="acc-title">&#10003; Acceptance of Offer — To Be Signed by Candidate</div>
    <p>
      I, <strong>{{employee.full_name}}</strong>, have read and fully understood the terms and
      conditions set forth in this Letter of Appointment dated <strong>{{today}}</strong>, issued
      by <strong>{{company.name}}</strong> for the position of
      <strong>{{#if employee.offered_designation}}{{employee.offered_designation}}{{else}}{{employee.designation}}{{/if}}</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
      I hereby <strong>unconditionally accept</strong> this offer and agree to be bound by all the
      terms, conditions, policies, and guidelines contained herein and as amended from time to time.
      I confirm that the information provided by me in my application and during the interview process
      is accurate, complete, and truthful. I understand that providing false information is grounds for
      immediate termination.
    </p>
    <p>
      I confirm my intent to join on
      <strong>{{#if employee.joining_date}}{{formatDate employee.joining_date "DD-MMM-YYYY"}}{{else}}{{formatDate employee.date_of_joining "DD-MMM-YYYY"}}{{/if}}</strong>
      and acknowledge that I have received a copy of this letter for my records.
    </p>
    <table class="acc-fields">
      <tr>
        <td>Candidate Signature</td>
        <td>Date of Acceptance</td>
        <td>Place</td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>

</div>

